# ShaibSport PWA — always push to GitHub

When working on the PWA at `~/Desktop/ShaipSportPWA` (repo `SouthArabia/ShaibSport`):

1. After making code/content changes, **commit and push to `origin/main`** without waiting to be asked.
2. Use `gh` as SouthArabia (or whatever account owns the repo). Remote: `https://github.com/SouthArabia/ShaibSport.git`
3. After push, trigger a Pages rebuild: `gh api -X POST repos/SouthArabia/ShaibSport/pages/builds`
4. Bump the service worker `CACHE` version in `sw.js` when shipping asset/JS changes so clients pick up updates.
5. Do not skip push for “small” fixes — keep GitHub Pages in sync with local work.
